About Us
If you're looking for a fun filled time, come down to Orleans Bistro & Bar! We have great Cajun food, burgers, wings, steaks, live music on Fridays & Saturdays, daily happy hour and menu items sure to please the entire family!
Hang out at the Bayou Bar for Pool, Darts and watch your favorite teams play.
Let The Good Times Roll!
Follow us on Facebook for all events and promotions.

Private Events
Come celebrate your birthdays, anniversaries, holidays and other events at our event room. Let us customize a catering package for you. With a full liquor bar and a capacity of up to seventy-five guests, you can be assured of a memorable event. Please contact the manager on duty for a tour.
